ed="T" n="0882c21"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0882c21"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>五臺山佛光寺<persName key="A013770">法興</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0882c22"/><persName key="A013770">釋法興</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛京</placeName>人也<ptr target="#n726"/>。七歲出家，不參流俗。執<lb
ed="T" n="0882c23"/>巾提盥，罔憚勤苦。諷念法華，年周部帙。<lb
ed="T" n="0882c24"/>又誦淨名經，匪逾九旬。戒律軌儀，有持無<lb
ed="T" n="0882c25"/>犯。來尋聖跡，樂止林泉，隷名<placeName key="PL000000005371">佛光寺</placeName>。節操<lb
ed="T" n="0882c26"/>孤頴，所霑利物，身不<anchor xml:id="beg0882005"/>主<anchor xml:id="end0882005"/>持，付屬門人。即修<lb
ed="T" n="0882c27"/>功德，建三層七間彌勒大閣，高九十五尺。尊<lb
ed="T" n="0882c28"/>像七十二位。聖賢、<persName key="G000035">八大龍王</persName>，罄從嚴飾。<placeName key="PL000000005250">臺山</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0882c29"/>海眾異舌同辭，請充山門都<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>焉</sic><corr>綱</corr></choice><ptr target="#n727"/>。蓋從其統<pb ed="T" n="0883a" xml:id="T50.2061.0883a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0883a01"/>攝，規範準繩，和暢無爭故也。<date key="j20235052023888" notAfter-iso="+0829-02-11" notBefore-iso="+0828-01-25"><name>大和</name>二年春正<lb
ed="T" n="0883a02"/>月</date>，聞空有聲云：「入滅時至，<placeName key="PL000000055446">兜率天</placeName>眾今來迎<lb
ed="T" n="0883a03"/>導。」於是洗浴<anchor xml:id="beg0883001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>梵</sic><corr>焚</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0883001"/>香，端坐入滅。建塔于<placeName key="PL000000005371">寺</placeName>西<lb
ed="T" n="0883a04"/>北一里所。</p>
